text: Hi Paula =) I only know how to upload videos from my computer the traditional way, using software like 'Debut.' It seems like you tried something new, right?

Hi Pia, to post a video clip first rewind to find to the start of the bit you want,   then click on the scissors symbol below bottom right of picture, a new box opens up.  i think it is 4 seconds to 60 seconds availability to record.  drag the slider box to the right to record your clip.  Name your clip. Click on share clip.  new box opens,  copy the link to your clipboard.   then open up your gallery and paste it.  voilà!
